    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Modifies code-page `.ts` types + parser; defines the contract consumed by tasks 041 + 042; carries ADR-022 (React 18) / ADR-026 / ADR-028 obligations.</rigor-reason>
